item.title: Anyone here?
item.dc:creator: @Motaro Motaro
item.description:
@Motaro wrote:

Put an existing sprites.rscd in the editor folder so you know where it is.

Unpack them, edit the unpacked .png files to whatever you want them to look like.

Run editor, press load picture and load the edited .png, press save sprite and save it to it’s correct ID with the extension .spr.

Put the .spr files you just created in the sprites folder.

Run packer, locate the sprites.rscd and done.
